<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }
        .header {
            background: #025864;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo-text {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .tagline {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 30px 40px 30px;
        }
        .notification-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .payment-info {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .amount-display {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #025864;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .amount-currency {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            vertical-align: super;
        }
        .receipt-details {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #025864;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #013a42;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                <tr>
                    <td align="center" valign="middle">
                        <svg width="24" height="32" viewBox="0 0 36 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="display: block;">
                            <path d="M0 7.5H28.8C31.3202 7.5 32.5804 7.5 33.543 7.99047C34.3897 8.4219 35.0781 9.11031 35.5095 9.95704C36 10.9196 36 12.1798 36 14.7V16.5H7.2C4.67976 16.5 3.41965 16.5 2.45704 16.0095C1.61031 15.5781 0.921901 14.8897 0.490471 14.043C0 13.0804 0 11.8202 0 9.3V7.5Z" fill="#D4F655"/>
                            <path d="M0 28.5H28.8C31.3202 28.5 32.5804 28.5 33.543 28.0095C34.3897 27.5781 35.0781 26.8897 35.5095 26.043C36 25.0804 36 23.8202 36 21.3V19.5H7.2C4.67976 19.5 3.41965 19.5 2.45704 19.9905C1.61031 20.4219 0.921901 21.1103 0.490471 21.957C0 22.9196 0 24.1798 0 26.7V28.5Z" fill="#D4F655"/>
                            <path d="M14 31.5H28.8C31.3202 31.5 32.5804 31.5 33.543 31.9905C34.3897 32.4219 35.0781 33.1103 35.5095 33.957C36 34.9196 36 36.1798 36 38.7V40.5H21.2C18.6798 40.5 17.4196 40.5 16.457 40.0095C15.6103 39.5781 14.9219 38.8897 14.4905 38.043C14 37.0804 14 35.8202 14 33.3V31.5Z" fill="#D4F655"/>
                        </svg>
                    </td>
                    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="padding-left: 12px;">
                        <span class="logo-text">RippliFy</span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="tagline">Secure Payment Links for Modern Businesses</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <span class="notification-badge">💰 Payment Received</span>
            </div>
            
            <h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0;">You've received a payment!</h2>
            
            <div class="payment-info">
                <p style="color: #64748b; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">Amount received from {{buyerName}}</p>
                <div style="margin: 10px 0;">
                    <span class="amount-currency">{{currency}}</span>
                    <span class="amount-display">{{amount}}</span>
                </div>
                <p style="color: #64748b; margin: 0; font-size: 12px;">Transaction ID: {{transactionId}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="receipt-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Product/Service</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{productName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Buyer Name</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{buyerName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{date}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Time</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{time}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Hello {{sellerName}},</p>
            
            <p>Great news! You received a payment from <strong>{{buyerName}}</strong>. The funds have been securely held in RippliFy escrow.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{viewOrdersUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Order Details</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <h3 style="color: #025864; font-size: 18px;">What happens next?</h3>
            
            <ul style="color: #475569; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li><strong>Funds Held</strong> - Payment is secure in escrow until delivery is confirmed</li>
                <li><strong>Process Order</strong> - Prepare and ship the product/service to the buyer</li>
                <li><strong>Mark as Shipped</strong> - Update the order status in your dashboard</li>
                <li><strong>Get Paid</strong> - Funds will be released once buyer confirms receipt</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, check your RippliFy dashboard for full transaction details.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The RippliFy Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{currentYear}} RippliFy. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>RippliFy Inc. | Nairobi, Kenya</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px;">
                <p>This email was sent to {{sellerEmail}} regarding payment {{transactionId}}.</p>
                <p><a href="#" style="color: #64748b;">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#" style="color: #64748b;">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#" style="color: #64748b;">Terms of Service</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>